            </div>
            <p>5G · 150 GB · Rete Vodafone · €5,99/mese</p>
          </div>
          <span class="tool-card-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="offers">
    <div class="offers-inner">
      <div class="offers-header">
        <span class="section-eyebrow section-eyebrow-light">🎯 Offerte</span>
        <h2>Offerte in evidenza</h2>
        <p>Selezionate dalla redazione · Aggiornate aprile 2026 · Condizioni verificate</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offers-grid">

        <div class="offer-card" style="--accent:#10b981;">
          <div class="offer-accent"></div>
          <div class="offer-head">
            <div class="offer-icon" style="background:#dcfce7;">💳</div>
            <div class="offer-names">
              <h3>BBVA Conto Online</h3>
